      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it looks and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feel without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
