      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior features a flawless, ceramic-coated finish with zero stone chips or swirl marks, while the interior remains in showroom condition, smelling fresh and showing absolutely no wear on the premium leather seating. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it has been exclusively dealer-serviced with a complete, organized history file included. Always climate-control garaged and never driven in inclement weather, this car performs exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title. For the buyer who demands perfection and a 'no-stories' vehicle, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
